---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Button from '../components/Button.astro';
import Card from '../components/Card.astro';
import Terminal from '../components/Terminal.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Team Orchestrator | Mission Control for Your Digital Workforce"
	description="Secure, auditable control plane for managing teams of AI agents with Athena as your strategic collaborator."
	ogType="website"
	twitterCard="summary"
>
	<section class="hero section-tight">
		<div class="container hero-grid hero-grid-stacked">
			<div>
				<p class="eyebrow">Governance for the Autonomous Era</p>
				<h1>Command your digital workforce.</h1>
				<p class="lead">
					Stop hoping for reliability. Start enforcing it. Team Orchestrator provides the secure, 
					auditable control plane engineering leaders need to govern specialist AI teams with absolute precision.
				</p>
				<div class="cta-row">
					<Button
						variant="primary"
						href="mailto:hello@teamorchestrator.com"
						analyticsEvent="cta_click"
						analyticsCategory="cta"
						analyticsLabel="request_early_access"
						analyticsLocation="home_hero"
					>
						Request Early Access
					</Button>
					<Button
						variant="secondary"
						href="/docs"
						analyticsEvent="docs_navigation_click"
						analyticsCategory="docs"
						analyticsLabel="explore_docs"
						analyticsLocation="home_hero"
					>
						Explore Docs
					</Button>
				</div>
			</div>
			<Terminal />
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section">
		<div class="container">
			<h2>Managed Autonomy. Mission-Grade Reliability.</h2>
			<div class="feature-grid">
				<Card>
					<h3>The Flight Director Model</h3>
					<p>
						You maintain strategic intent. Athena—your orchestrator—translates that intent into 
						executable plans, manages specialists, and handles complex handoffs.
					</p>
				</Card>
				<Card>
					<h3>Context Compounding</h3>
					<p>
						Eliminate agentic drift. Intelligence is distilled and compounded through every mission 
						relay, ensuring every specialist starts with perfect situational awareness.
					</p>
				</Card>
				<Card>
					<h3>Systemic Governance</h3>
					<p>
						Auditability is the foundation. Every decision is traced and every mission is bound 
						by policy-aware execution and industrial-grade observability.
					</p>
				</Card>
				<Card>
					<h3>The Override Key</h3>
					<p>
						True autonomy requires control. Approve, modify, or reject flight plans at any stage. 
						The agents run the work; you hold the steering.
					</p>
				</Card>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section alt">
		<div class="container">
			<h2>The Mission Lifecycle</h2>
			<ol class="steps">
				<li>
					<h3>1. Objective Interpretation</h3>
					<p>
						Define the mission. Athena analyzes requirements and proposes a deterministic path 
						leveraging the optimal sequence of specialist agents.
					</p>
				</li>
				<li>
					<h3>2. Unit Deployment</h3>
					<p>
						Validate the flight plan. Athena provisions secure environments, briefs the 
						specialists, and initiates the governed execution loop.
					</p>
				</li>
				<li>
					<h3>3. Contextual Relay</h3>
					<p>
						As tasks conclude, Athena distills outputs into high-density context for the next 
						specialist, preserving the integrity of the mission across handoffs.
					</p>
				</li>
				<li>
					<h3>4. Mission Briefing</h3>
					<p>
						Receive a comprehensive evidence bundle and strategic summary. The loop only 
						closes once the Flight Director verifies the objective is met.
					</p>
				</li>
			</ol>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section">
		<div class="container split">
			<Card>
				<h2>Operational modes</h2>
				<p><strong>Silent Run:</strong> Athena manages specialist execution and returns with outcomes.</p>
				<p><strong>Active Bridge:</strong> Real-time collaborative sessions for planning and strategy.</p>
			</Card>
			<Card>
				<h2>Command surface</h2>
				<p><strong class="tech-label">CLI:</strong> <code>athena run</code></p>
				<p><strong class="tech-label">State:</strong> <code>.athena/</code></p>
				<p><strong class="tech-label">Identity Header:</strong> <code>X-Athena-Identity</code></p>
			</Card>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section alt">
		<div class="container">
			<h2>Current trajectory</h2>
			<p class="lead compact">Team Orchestrator is currently in Stage 8 (in progress).</p>
			<div class="roadmap-grid">
				<Card><h3>Foundation</h3><p>Mission Control backend.</p></Card>
				<Card><h3>Mission Relay</h3><p>A2A coordination and context compounding.</p></Card>
				<Card><h3>The Hangar</h3><p>Sandboxing, swarm provisioning, and PDK.</p></Card>
				<Card><h3>Command Bridge</h3><p>Dashboard and Athena strategic HUD.</p></Card>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
